Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在悄无声息中燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何一个人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经改变 被红世的火炎包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的将力量传给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『悠二和夏娜和接吻』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经能很轻易的形成翅膀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜已经到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然力量能恢复是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉还是有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要适应它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下面吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧的重播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是编故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要关掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理恵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很痛的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他会被打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的人如果突然被人吻 一定会不愿意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是接吻嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...都在看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕 迪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你们的行为和显眼的打扮才引起他人注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵盛放之时为何要掩饰自己的美丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修德奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在我的『摇篮之园』的保护下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不希望你这么拽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 迪莉娅 我可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要再等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像马上就要找到哥哥想找的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到了 如果被谁给拿走了岂不是亏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让人发现 就把这里封锁起来 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们的『摇篮之园』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把除了那个以外的都吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你知道orgel吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,orgel？ 是八音盒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 一般是这样称呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是叫它“orgel” 不感觉更成熟优雅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是和这个自在式一起用来建造摇篮用的宝具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这美丽的旋律听的我都要流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候玩什么躲避球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下的真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还好中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再继续下去的话 一定会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大...大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看伤的不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于平井的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你们经常一起上学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们之间有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然嘴上说什么“不就接吻嘛”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真做起来就不容易了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然肯了 不过过会儿还是很尴尬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 接吻 应该是很珍重的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天提到这个 悠二的感觉有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书上说的应该不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在查什么资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 并不是什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是和平井关系好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有恋爱关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头 我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了啊 我头都要炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上的伤怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被球砸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点不想喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻 有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 为什么要问这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来简单 但又复杂的问题啊 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你查过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去图书馆查书 也都是些常识性的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么接吻我也知道 也看到过 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉大家对接吻的认识和我对其的认识完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 千草可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有看小说和文学书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果带有个人的主观意识\N对准确的分析和理论性的思考就起不了一点作用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯托尔这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯托尔 是你在远方的类似你父亲一般的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有很广博的见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 你这样就不会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记载在书籍上的 只是记述先世的事实和理论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 夏娜要考虑的正是这以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是含含糊糊 没有正确答案的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是心灵和感情的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵和感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互接触对方身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是相互间爱情的产生 这你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻也属于其中一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和握手 拥抱什么的一样吧 大家都是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说这和阿拉斯托尔先生做是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能和小悠做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新想一想 是不是感觉很难为情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是重点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻 和亲吻和嘴对嘴还是有很大区别的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和...悠二 嘴对嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是能和阿拉斯托尔做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴和嘴的接吻就如同誓言一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的一切都融于对方也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的一切都交付于人也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 稍微有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为“零时迷子”的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量只要一到零点就能恢复是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是说不会变老了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会花费很长的时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想会不会和夏娜永远在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事情要拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草 借你的电话用用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是夏娜 已经到上学的时间了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 换我接电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 自我介绍下 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名叫阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你就是阿拉斯托尔先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直蒙您照顾平井由香里同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是坂井悠二的母亲 千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是给你们添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊 没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什么重要的事情吗 特地要打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井由香里同学的事的话 我很乐意和您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你称呼她夏娜也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经常这么叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯托尔先生已经是很拗口的名字了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我想和你谈的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是关于昨天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠 夏娜 快去上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不想否定夫人您的恋爱观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是希望你别再说和昨天那样的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜和你说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我硬要她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜愿意和我谈这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是她非常信任我的证明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在很细心地抚养夏娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个非常纯真的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你注意一下象昨天那样\N诱发夏娜和坂井悠二发生不谨慎接触的言论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白您的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人真是明见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我也没什么疑虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于夏娜 能再和你谈会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个高贵 顽强的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她身上还有些幼稚脆弱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您继续说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到夏娜对人的感情和心灵方面\N有些特别不习惯和不谨慎的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的悠二刚开始遇见年轻有活力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁无暇的那个孩子 也是挡不住诱惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我感觉到这种危险 所以才和她谈了这个事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不感觉太早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花上漫长的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她体验各种各样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的教她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不对我们有利的话是不会去冒险的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我把应该教的教给她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这不算太早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了夏娜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她比她的外表看来更早熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能撤回刚才提出的愚昧要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我该道歉才是 说了一些过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要好好教那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会用自己的方式找到正确的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你应该相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近了 近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像在找什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索拉德的“欲望之嗅觉”真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这心烦的感觉 绝对是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 在哪 火雾战士 我好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该感觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道遇上火雾战士也只是时间上的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你准备怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想再准备周全些的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开始吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先去打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找到她太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊 刚才阿拉斯托尔在电话里说昨天怎么怎么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 绝对 不会和你那个的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是给坂井同学做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你总是吃饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不定主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你买了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止[不少]啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,购物才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦的时候 又来了几个了不得的客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的杀虐者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么呢 娘娘腔帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我介绍你们认识 迪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火雾战士中也是首屈一指的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛经的咏唱者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛吉莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是蹂躏之爪牙的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人没有我想要的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想怎么这么容易就找到了 结果不是猎物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要 哥哥这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是红世之徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过他们没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是放过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被他们放过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 笨蛋马尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你和妈妈说了些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不用你关心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 你要多加修炼 不要给母亲丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠 夏娜 饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会和你那个的
